OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FA judge has made clear he will be
OL,7,F"extremely disappointed" if the
OL,8,Fhistorical sexual offences trial of
OL,9,Fformer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,10,FDonaldson does not proceed on May 26
OL,11,Fas scheduled.
OL,13,FProceedings against Donaldson and his
OL,14,Fwife Lady Eleanor Donaldson have been
OL,15,Fdelayed twice due to medical issues
OL,16,Frelated to her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
