PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FA review hearing in Newry Crown Court
OL,7,Fon Tuesday was told that one further
OL,8,Fmedical assessments of Eleanor
OL,9,FDonaldson still had to be carried out
OL,10,Fahead of the trial date later this
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FJudge Paul Ramsey acknowledged that
OL,14,F"genuine medical evidence" remained
OL,15,Foutstanding but he said it was
OL,16,Fnevertheless his "expectation rather
OL,17,Fthan hope" that a trial would commence
OL,18,Fas scheduled on May 26.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@ZO]xD@ROUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FHe listed another review hearing for
OL,7,FMay 19 to enable all parties to the
OL,8,Fcase to assess the findings of the
OL,9,Fadditional examinations and determine
OL,10,Fwhether they would influence how
OL,11,Fproceedings would progress.
OL,13,FJeffrey Donaldson, 63, has pleaded not
OL,14,Fguilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,16,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,17,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,18,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,19,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008,
OL,20,Finvolving two alleged victims.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FEleanor Donaldson, 60, and from
OL,7,FDromore, is facing charges of aiding
OL,8,Fand abetting, which she denies.
OL,10,FNeither of the Donaldsons attended
OL,11,FTuesday's hearing in Newry courthouse.
OL,13,FProsecuting barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,14,FKC told the court that she had
OL,15,Fprovided a position paper to all
OL,16,Fparties setting out two options on how
OL,17,Fthe case could progress if Eleanor
OL,18,FDonaldson is deemed unfit for trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FEleanor Donaldson's counsel Ian
OL,7,FTurkington KC insisted other options
OL,8,Fwould also need to be considered in
OL,9,Fthat scenario.
OL,11,FMr Turkington said there was "cogent
OL,12,Fmedical evidence" in relation to the
OL,13,F"unfitness" of his client and insisted
OL,14,Fit would be "grossly unfair" to
OL,15,Fcommence a trial against her if she
OL,16,Fwas not in condition to participate in
OL,17,Fit.
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@QO]uD@AOUuD@KO]vD@MOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FThe judge said all parties were
OL,7,Ftalking "in a bit of a vacuum" until
OL,8,Fthey had sight of the two medical
OL,9,Fassessments.
OL,11,F"I really would be extremely
OL,12,Fdisappointed if this case did not
OL,13,Fproceed on the 26th of May," he said.
OL,15,FThe judge acknowledged the May 19
OL,16,Freview hearing meant "quite a short
OL,17,Fturnaround" for parties to consider
OL,18,Fthe medical evidence ahead of the
OL,19,Fscheduled trial start date.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@^O]sD@AOUuD@\O]xD@VOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,FBut he said the court would be clearer
OL,7,Fon the "path forward" after the review
OL,8,Fhearing.
OL,10,FHe said he realised there was some
OL,11,Fpublic concern over the "apparent
OL,12,Fdelay" in the case.
OL,14,F"But there is genuine medical evidence
OL,15,Fhere in this case that we have to look
OL,16,Fat and we have to consider before we
OL,17,Fcan proceed," he added.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@UO]sD@YOUtD@FO]vD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778155868
OL,3,C'Expectation' Donaldson trial to begin
OL,4,Clater this month
OL,6,F"But I think every effort must be made
OL,7,Fto expedite that so that we're ready
OL,8,Fto go on the 26th of May, because I
OL,9,Fthink it's in the interest of all
OL,10,Fparties that the case should commence."
OL,12,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,13,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,14,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,15,FMarch 2024.
OL,17,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,18,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,19,Fallegations emerged.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
